videoSnippet.title: Dr. Gregory House vs Arrogant Chess Prodigy Nate
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator For those of you that like to watch the show "House", there was one episode involving chess.  Dr. Gregory House (Hugh Laurie with an amazing American accent) played this arrogant chess prodigy in a very well-done scene.

Young Evil Prodigy Nate vs Dr. Gregory House
The Bird-Sicilian opening :D

1. f4 c5 2. Nf3 d5 3. e3 Nf6 4. b3 e6 5. Ba3 Bd6 6. Bb5+ Nc6 7. Nc3 O-O 8. Rb1 e5 9. fxe5 Nxe5 10. Be2 Ne4 11. Nxd5 Nxf3+ 12. Bxf3 Qh4+ 13. g3 Bxg3+ 14. hxg3 Qxg3+ 15. Ke2 Ng5 16. Qf1 Nxf3 17. Qxf3 Bg4 18. Ne7+ Kh8 19. Rxh7+ Kxh7 20. Rh1+ Bh5 21. Qxh5#
